OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FFeted Finnish composer     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FKaija Saariaho dies at 70  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Finnish composer Kaija Saariaho,       
OL,6, considered to be an innovator in       
OL,7, classical music, has died aged 70.     
OL,9,FHer family said she had been diagnosed 
OL,10,Fin 2021 with an aggressive form of     
OL,11,Fbrain cancer and had kept her illness  
OL,12,Fprivate to focus on her work.          
OL,14,FHer early work included an acclaimed   
OL,15,Fviolin concerto but her international  
OL,16,Fbreakthrough came with her debut opera 
OL,17,FL'Amour de loin in 2000.               
OL,19,FPeter Sellars, who directed it, spoke  
OL,20,Fof the "secret beauty" of her music.   
